<br>
besides knowledge and situational awareness  you need to learn the limits of OTHER CLASSES . you will group with may other classes and each has its strenghts and weeknesses just like warriors but we need to know them as well. especialy when it comes to chanters clerics shaman and wizards.<br>
the one most tanks tend to leave out is wizards because they Usualy control agro well unless you get a bad one which i will admit there are a few.<br>
<br>
any ways thats my 2 bits o silver. BUT AS everyone here agrees knowledge ,situational awareness , initutive and balls are very important too. just thought i would throw this last on about Other classes limits too just to round things out and make it all complete =)<br>
